snippet.title: The World Ends with You: Final Remix - Teaser Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
This definitive version of Square Enix’s RPG classic brings the dark story to life, coming to the Nintendo Switch system on October 12, 2018.

Learn more about The World Ends with You: Final Remix! https://goo.gl/XZTz2A
